column2: SELECT n.objid, m.rmapid, m.ra as ra, m.dec as dec, s.z as z_spec, m.z_lambda as zlambda, m.lambda as lambda, m.mstar as mstar, s.velDisp, s.velDispZ, o.deVRad_r, o.deVAB_r, o.deVPhi_r, o.deVMag_r, o.petroR9#_r, o.petroR5#_r, n.distance, m.p_cen0 as p_cen, m.Dn4# as Dn4#, m.HdeltaA as HdeltaA, m.MtoLz as MtoLz, m.logAge as logAge, m.muxtau as muxtau, m.Metal as Metal, m.Fracstar as Fracstar into mydb.MyTable_radius_mstar from myDB.redmapper_mstar as m cross apply dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) as n join Galaxy as o on n.objid = o.objID join SpecObj as s on n.objid = s.bestobjID
